sequenceDiagram
    participant Input as Text
    participant Tok as Tokenizer
    participant Enc as Encoder
    participant Soft as Softmax
    participant Dec as Decoder

    Input->>Tok: document

    Note over Tok: Sliding window<br/>stride=382, overlap=128

    loop for each window
        Tok->>Enc: input_ids, attention_mask
        Enc->>Enc: 12× Transformer blocks
        Enc->>Soft: logits z ∈ ℝ^(n×41)

        Note over Soft: pᵢ = softmax(zᵢ)<br/>H = -Σ p log p<br/>c = max(p)

        Soft->>Dec: predictions + H, c
    end

    Note over Dec: Merge overlapping<br/>windows

    Dec-->>Input: BIO labels per token

    Note over Input: Entity extraction<br/>from BIO sequence
